    { id: 'muniz-kpi-3', longTermGoal: 'Decrease chronic absenteeism from 43.5% to below 40%   As of 4/7/2026 Today’s Attendance: 90.64% Year-to-Date Attendance: 89.8% Attendance is consistently approaching 90%, showing steady improvement, though still below the 94% target. Evidence of Impact Attendance Trends Fall 2025: 83.9% – 93% (inco', intervention: '3. Targeted Student Supports (Tier 2 & 3) SST Grade-Level Teams Ongoing attendance review by Crew/Grade Assignment of attendance “champions” Case Management System Students with attendance, academic, or wellness concerns are assigned case managers Monitoring and intervention planning is ongoing Tier 3 Supports Panorama Plans for chronically absent students Individualized interventions and progress', goalDate: '', midpoint: '', status: 'Not Started', pct: 0, endline: '' },
    { id: 'muniz-kpi-4', longTermGoal: 'Decrease chronic absenteeism from 43.5% to below 40%   As of 4/7/2026 Today’s Attendance: 90.64% Year-to-Date Attendance: 89.8% Attendance is consistently approaching 90%, showing steady improvement, though still below the 94% target. Evidence of Impact Attendance Trends Fall 2025: 83.9% – 93% (inco', intervention: '4. Engagement & Accountability Strategies Grade-level competitions (e.g., March Madness Challenge) Athletics reinforcing attendance expectations Consideration/use of attendance contracts CPT meetings reviewing attendance by Crew Leader  Coordinator Role: Able to come together with the attendance team & come with ideas, encourage students, whether it is teachers & incentives, help engage in that; o', goalDate: '', midpoint: '', status: 'Not Started', pct: 0, endline: '' },
    { id: 'muniz-kpi-5', longTermGoal: 'Decrease chronic absenteeism from 43.5% to below 40%   As of 4/7/2026 Today’s Attendance: 90.64% Year-to-Date Attendance: 89.8% Attendance is consistently approaching 90%, showing steady improvement, though still below the 94% target. Evidence of Impact Attendance Trends Fall 2025: 83.9% – 93% (inco', intervention: 'Monitoring & Evidence Artifacts Daily attendance call logs (JR entries) Attendance Team meeting notes + data analysis SST Grade Team notes Case manager assignments and progress reports Tier 3 Panorama Plans   Coordinator Role: Compare Aspen & Jump Rope, report/ attendance call sheet; & then the coordinator goes in Jump Rope to make sure it is consistent across, in Jump Rope & Aspen. The attendance', goalDate: '', midpoint: '', status: 'Not Started', pct: 0, endline: '' }
