    { id: 'holland-kpi-6', longTermGoal: 'Decrease the number of chronic absenteeism by  2.5% by June, 2026', intervention: 'senior attendance night: Our senior class has played a significant role in increasing overall school attendance, representing 150 of our 570 students and demonstrating consistent commitment throughout their high school years. As a key subgroup within our attendance KPI, their engagement has positively influenced school-wide attendance trends and culture.', goalDate: '', midpoint: 'To sustain this momentum and recognize their impact, we are requesting $1,200 to host a Senior Night that celebrates their attendance, perseverance, and growth, while also honoring their families for their ongoing support. This event will reinforce the importance of consistent attendance, strengthen', status: 'Not Started', pct: 0, endline: '' }
